Barry Bonds’s Lawyers Want Jurors Told to Ignore Prosecutors' Statement

-- B y   K a r e n   G u l l o
-- 
2011-04-08T17:39:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-08/barry-bonds-s-lawyers-want-jurors-told-to-ignore-prosecutors-statement.html
Attorneys for baseball player  Barry
Bonds  asked a federal judge to recall the jury deliberating
perjury charges against the slugger and instruct them to ignore
a prosecutor’s statement that Bonds knew the difference between
a designer steroid and flaxseed oil, according to a court
filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Karen Gullo in  San Francisco  at 
 kgullo@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
